OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776690659
OL,3,CRobot wins Beijing half marathon,
OL,4,Cbeating human world record
OL,6,FA robot that won a half-marathon race
OL,7,Fin Beijing on Sunday ran faster than
OL,8,Fthe human world record in a show of
OL,9,FChina's technological leaps.
OL,11,FIt was the second time Beijing has
OL,12,Fhosted the robot-only half-marathon
OL,13,Faimed at displaying the prowess of
OL,14,FChinese robotics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
