FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776690659
OL,3,CRobot wins Beijing half marathon,
OL,4,Cbeating human world record
OL,6,FThe winner from Honor, a Chinese
OL,7,Fsmartphone maker, completed the 13-
OL,8,Fmile race in 50 minutes and 26
OL,9,Fseconds, according to a WeChat post by
OL,10,Fthe Beijing Economic-Technological
OL,11,FDevelopment Area, also known as
OL,12,FBeijing E-Town, where the race kicked
OL,13,Foff.
OL,15,FThat was faster than the human world
OL,16,Frecord holder, Uganda's Jacob Kiplimo,
OL,17,Fwho finished the same distance in
OL,18,Fabout 57 minutes in March at the
OL,19,FLisbon road race.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776690659
OL,3,CRobot wins Beijing half marathon,
OL,4,Cbeating human world record
OL,6,FLast year's robotic winner won the
OL,7,Frace in 2 hours, 40 minutes and 42
OL,8,Fseconds
OL,10,FBut the competition, which was held
OL,11,Falongside a race for humans, wasn't
OL,12,Fwithout hiccups ` one robot fell flat
OL,13,Fat the start line, another bumped into
OL,14,Fa barrier.
OL,16,FDu Xiaodi, Honor's test development
OL,17,Fengineer, said his team was happy with
OL,18,Fthe results.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776690659
OL,3,CRobot wins Beijing half marathon,
OL,4,Cbeating human world record
OL,6,FDu said its robot design was modelled
OL,7,Fon outstanding human athletes, with
OL,8,Flong legs of about 95cm, and was
OL,9,Fequipped with what he called a
OL,10,Fpowerful liquid-cooling system, which
OL,11,Fwas largely developed in-house.
OL,13,F"Looking ahead, some of these
OL,14,Ftechnologies might be transferred to
OL,15,Fother areas. For example, structural
OL,16,Freliability and liquid-cooling
OL,17,Ftechnology could be applied in future
OL,18,Findustrial scenarios," he said.
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
