FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776690659
OL,3,CRobot wins Beijing half marathon,
OL,4,Cbeating human world record
OL,6,FWhile it will still take time to
OL,7,Fachieve widespread commercialisation
OL,8,Fof humanoid robots, spectators were
OL,9,Falready impressed by the robots. Sun
OL,10,FZhigang, who had been in the audience
OL,11,Flast year, watched Sunday's race with
OL,12,Fhis son.
OL,14,F"I feel enormous changes this year,"
OL,15,FSun said. "It's the first time robots
OL,16,Fhave surpassed humans, and that's
OL,17,Fsomething I never imagined."
OL,26,@vD@AOUvD@dO]wD@KOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
