PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776690659
OL,3,CRobot wins Beijing half marathon,
OL,4,Cbeating human world record
OL,6,FWang Wen, who came with his family,
OL,7,Fsaid robots seemed to have stolen much
OL,8,Fof the spotlight from human runners in
OL,9,Fthe event.
OL,11,F"The robots' speed far exceeds that of
OL,12,Fhumans," he said. "This may signal the
OL,13,Farrival of sort of a new era."
OL,15,FBeijing E-Town said about 40% of the
OL,16,Frobots navigated the course
OL,17,Fautonomously, while the others were
OL,18,Fremotely controlled.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@HO]tD@SOUuD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
