PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776690659
OL,3,CRobot wins Beijing half marathon,
OL,4,Cbeating human world record
OL,6,FState media outlet Global Times
OL,7,Freported that a separate, remotely-
OL,8,Fcontrolled robot from Honor was the
OL,9,Ffirst to cross the finish line in 48
OL,10,Fminutes and 19 seconds.
OL,12,FBut it said the winning one used
OL,13,Fautonomous navigation and received the
OL,14,Fchampionship under the event's
OL,15,Fweighted scoring rules.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
