OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776690659
OL,3,CRobot wins Beijing half marathon,
OL,4,Cbeating human world record
OL,6,FState broadcaster CCTV reported that
OL,7,Fthe runners-up, which were also from
OL,8,FHonor and used autonomous navigation,
OL,9,Ffinished the race in about 51 minutes
OL,10,Fand 53 minutes, respectively. A robot
OL,11,Fserved as a traffic officer to direct
OL,12,Fthe participants with its arm gestures
OL,13,Fand voice, CCTV added.
OL,15,FThe display shows how China is pulling
OL,16,Fahead of other players, including
OL,17,FEurope and the US, in the world of
OL,18,Frobotics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
