PN,30709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1776690659
OL,3,CRobot wins Beijing half marathon,
OL,4,Cbeating human world record
OL,6,FLondon-based technology research and
OL,7,Fadvisory group Omdia recently ranked
OL,8,Fthree Chinese companies ` AGIBOT,
OL,9,FUnitree Robotics and UBTech Robotics
OL,10,FCorp. - as the only first-tier vendors
OL,11,Fin its global assessment for shipment
OL,12,Fnumbers for general-purpose embodied
OL,13,Fintelligent robots.
OL,15,FThey all shipped more than 1,000 units
OL,16,Fof the robots last year, with the
OL,17,Ffirst two companies shipping more than
OL,18,F5,000 units, the report said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
